elems.code:
{
	// Users can see ads posted by everyone, 
	// but only see non ads posted by followed users.
	all u : User, p : Photo | u->p in sees implies p in Ad or
  	some u1 : User | u1->p in posts and u->u1 in follows
  
  	all u : User, a : Photo | u->a in sees implies a in Ad or
  	some u1 : User | u1 in posts.a and u1 in u.follows
  
  	all u : User, a : Photo | u->a in sees implies a in Ad or
  	some u1 : User | u1 in (posts.a & u.follows)
  
  	all u : User, a : Photo | u->a in sees implies a in Ad or
  	some posts.a & u.follows
  
  	all u : User, a : Photo | a in u.sees implies a in Ad or
  	some posts.a & u.follows
  
  	all u : User, a : u.sees | a in Ad or some posts.a & u.follows
  
  	all u : User, a : u.sees-Ad | some posts.a & u.follows
}

{
  
  all u: User | all a: Ad | a in u.sees
  and
  
  all u: User | all p: Photo - Ad | p in u.sees implies (some u2: User | p in u2.posts and u2 in u.follows)
  and
  
  all u: User | all p: Photo | p in u.sees implies (some u2: User | p in u2.posts)
}
